      ## Exercise - playing with cats
      Now you can play with your Cat.

      Try out the following commands in the console:

    :ruby
      code = <<-CODE
      c = Cat.create name: "Markey"
      Cat.all
      c.name = "Dave"
      c.save
      Cat.first
      Cat.first.name
      Cat.find(1)
      CODE
    =code(code, :ruby)

    :markdown

      What do they all do? You can do all this in your controller.

