      ## Exercise - A basket full of tiny little cats

      Now create 10 more cats, and try out the following.

    :ruby
      code = <<-CODE
      Cat.order(:name)
      Cat.order(:name).limit(5)
      Cat.where(name: "Dave")
      Cat.where("created_at > ?", Time.now - 1.minute)
      Cat.count
      CODE
    =code(code, :ruby)

